data.description: Taste Plus Space!!!  Popular Mirada design has sensible touches everywhere.  Well- proportioned rooms mean easy living. This corner lot offers easy access to the Golf Course, Grill, Community pool, Spa and Workout facility.  Updated Kitchen with Newer Stainless Steel appliances, Granite Countertops , Spacious Island, plenty of cabinet space and a Walk in Pantry.   Covered Extended Patio with Built in Grill and Water Feature.  Come take a look at this well-maintained home, 45+ Gated Community in the Center of Corte Bella..
